    {
        "url": "/quotes/patrick_m_byrne_851322",
        "quote": "Over the next decade, there will be disruption as significant as the Internet was for publishing, where blockchain is going to disrupt dozens of industries, one being capital markets and Wall Street.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Patrick M. Byrne",
            "url": "/quotes/patrick_m_byrne_851322"
