                "name": "Chain",
                "url": "/topics/chain"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/patrick_m_byrne_851341",
        "quote": "You're going to start seeing open-source, self-executing contracts gradually improve over time. What the Internet did to publishing, blockchain will do to about 160 different industries. It's crazy.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Patrick M. Byrne",
            "url": "/quotes/patrick_m_byrne_851341"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Going",
                "url": "/topics/going"
