    {
        "url": "/quotes/patrick_m_byrne_851329",
        "quote": "There are regulators at the SEC and elsewhere who are really excited about the potential of the blockchain. They understand you can build a robust financial system - it would solve all your black swan problems. All kinds of mischief and games that are played in the current system become impossible in this system.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Patrick M. Byrne",
            "url": "/quotes/patrick_m_byrne_851329"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Impossible",
